snippet.title: Animals, our best and funniest little furry friends - Funny animal compilation
snippet.description:
Animals can always cheer us up and make us laugh. They are so funny and cute! Just look at all these hilarious cats, kittens, dogs, puppies, cows, ducks, giraffes... What is your favourite clip? ;) Hope you like our compilation, please share it and SUBSCRIBE! Watch also our other videos!

WANT TO SEE YOUR PET IN OUR COMPILATIONS?
Send your clips or links to: tigerlicensing@gmail.com

For more funny videos & pictures visit and like our Facebook page:
https://www.facebook.com/tigerstudiosfun

The content in this compilation is licensed through our agreement with network.
 
FREE MUSIC USED:
"Upbeat Forever, Monkeys Spinning Monkeys" Kevin MacLeod (incompetech.com)
